==描述==
[[File:Felis-speleata_Höhlenlöwe.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Lascaux-diverticule-félins.jpg|thumb]]上的穴獅]]
穴獅時在[[舊石器時代|舊石器時代]]常以[[石洞壁畫|石洞壁畫]]、[[象牙|象牙]]雕刻、[[黏土|黏土]]{{link-en|塑像|figurine}}的形式呈現，這些[[遺物|遺物]]代表著穴獅也可能出現於舊石器時代的宗教[[儀式|儀式]]當中<ref>{{cite book |authors=Bahn, P. G., Vertut, J. |year=1997 |title=Journey Through the Ice Age |url=https://archive.org/details/journeythroughic00bahn |publisher=Weidenfeld & Nicolson |location=London}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author=Guthrie, R. D. |year=2005 |title=The Nature of Paleolithic Art |publisher=University of Chicago Press |location=Chicago}}</ref>。在[[法國|法國]][[肖维岩洞|肖维岩洞]]（約 30,000 年前）描繪了一對走在一起的穴獅，其中一隻的體型略小於另一隻，而體型較大的個體則繪有[[陰囊|陰囊]]，但不具有鬃毛<ref name=Yamaguchietal2004>{{Cite journal |last1=Yamaguchi |first1=N. | last2=Cooper |first2=A. |last3=Werdelin |first3=L. |last4= MacDonald |first4=D. W. |date=2004 |title=Evolution of the mane and group-living in the lion (''Panthera leo''): a review |journal=Journal of Zoology |volume=263 |issue=4 |pages=329–342 |doi=10.1017/S0952836904005242}}</ref>。這代表穴獅和現代獅子不一樣，牠們可能不具有明顯的鬃毛<ref name=Stuart2011/>。

在被獨立為一種時，穴獅曾是獅子所有亞種中体格最大的之一，1985 年在[[德國|德國]][[锡格斯多夫|锡格斯多夫]]附近發現的一只成年雄性洞穴獅化石表明，其及肩身高約{{convert|1.2|m|ft|abbr=on}}，身長{{convert|2.1|m|ft|abbr=on}}（不含尾巴），這大致相當于一頭體型相當大的現代獅子。實際上，這只洞穴獅並不是同類中最大的，因此可以推斷，洞穴獅要比現代獅子大5%到10%，但比較早期的[[原始獅|原始獅]]（''Panthera fossilis''）還有之後的[[美洲擬獅|美洲擬獅]]小<ref>Koenigswald, W. v. (2002). Lebendige Eiszeit. Darmstadt: Theiss-Wissenschaftliche Buchgemeinschaft. {{ISBN|3-8062-1734-3}}</ref>。和現代獅子一樣，雌獅的體型較雄獅小<ref>{{cite journal |author=Diedrich, C. G. |year=2011 |title=Late Pleistocene ''Panthera leo spelaea'' (Goldfuss, 1810) skeletons from the Czech Republic (central Europe); their pathological cranial features and injuries resulting from intraspecific fights, conflicts with hyenas, and attacks on cave bears |journal=Bulletin of Geosciences |volume=86 |issue=4 |pages=817–840 |doi=10.3140/bull.geosci.1263 }}</ref>

==古生態學==
穴獅生活在一些開闊的環境如{{link-en|猛獁草原|mammoth steppe}}或是[[北方針葉林|北方針葉林]]。牠們的骨骼多半與[[洞鬣狗|洞鬣狗]]、[[洞熊|洞熊]]和[[舊石器時代|舊石器時代]]文物一同在洞穴中發現因而得名<ref>{{cite journal |author=Diedrich, C. G. |year=2011 |title=The largest European lion ''Panthera leo spelaea'' (Goldfuss 1810) population from the Zoolithen Cave, Germany: specialised cave bear predators of Europe |journal=Historical Biology |volume=23 |issue=2–3 |pages=271–311 |url= |doi=10.1080/08912963.2010.546529}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Diedrich, C. G.  |year=2011 |title=Pleistocene ''Panthera leo spelaea'' (Goldfuss 1810) remains from the Balve cave (NW Germany) - a cave bear, hyena den and middle palaeolithic human cave – and review of the Sauerland Karst lion cave sites |journal=Quaternaire |volume=22 |issue=2 |pages=105–127 |url=}}</ref>。穴獅可能為獨居性的掠食者<ref>{{cite journal |author=Bocherens, H. |year=2015 |title=Isotopic tracking of large carnivore palaeoecology in the mammoth steppe |journal=Quaternary Science Reviews |volume=117 |issue= |pages=42–71 |url= |doi=10.1016/j.quascirev.2015.03.018}}</ref>。

從化石中[[膠原蛋白|膠原蛋白]]樣本的[[同位素|同位素]]分析顯示穴獅主要以洞熊幼崽、[[馴鹿|馴鹿]]與其他[[鹿科|鹿科]]為主食，尤其是馴鹿<ref name=Bocherens>{{cite journal |authors=Bocherens, H., Drucker, D. G., Bonjean, D., Bridault, A., Conard, N. J., Cupillard, C., Germonpré, M., Höneisen, M., Münzel, S. C., Napierala, H., and Patou-Mathis, M. |date=2011 |title=Isotopic evidence for dietary ecology of cave lion (''Panthera spelaea'') in North-Western Europe: prey choice, competition and implications for extinction |journal=Quaternary International |volume=245 |issue=2 |pages=249–261 |url=https://www.academia.edu/download/38252429/BOCHERENS___al_2011QI-lion.pdf |doi=10.1016/j.quaint.2011.02.023 }}{{Dead link|date=September 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。其他可能的獵物包括[[大角鹿|大角鹿]]、[[歐洲馬鹿|歐洲馬鹿]]、[[麝牛|麝牛]]、[[西伯利亞野牛|西伯利亞野牛]]、幼年[[披毛犀|披毛犀]]以及幼年[[猛獁象|猛獁象]]<ref name=Stuart2011/>。

